  <summary date="2021-06-21T17:02:15Z" status="Introduced in Senate">I Am Vanessa Guillen Act

This bill addresses the response of the Department of Defense to sex-related offenses committed against members of the Armed Forces, including allowing a member to confidentially allege a complaint of sexual harassment to an individual outside the immediate chain of command of that member.</summary>
